        <Parent_String>crinolines [300210554], underwear and accessories for shaping and supporting [300209268], underwear [300209267], clothing [300266639], costume (mode of fashion) [300178802], Costume (hierarchy name) [300209261], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
